name: bakllava
description: BakLLaVA is a multimodal model consisting of the Mistral 7B base model augmented with the LLaVA  architecture.
readme_html:
Note: this model requires Ollama 0.1.15: download it here

CLI Usage

Run the model:

ollama run bakllava

Then at the prompt, include the path to your image in the prompt:

>>> What's in this image? /Users/jmorgan/Desktop/smile.png
The image features a yellow smiley face, which is likely the central focus of the picture.

API Usage

curl http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d '{
  "model": "bakllava",
  "prompt":"What is in this picture?",
  "images": [""]
}'

References

GitHub

HuggingFace
